From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Radxa Overlay Maintainers <overlay@example.invalid>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 15:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: cix: restore Sky1 DT binding headers

The Sky1 6.18 DTS patch references several binding headers that lived in
Sky1's infrastructure patch. This overlay skips that infrastructure patch
because the CIX 6.18 patch queue carries the driver code, but the CIX queue
does not provide every DTS-only header that the board device trees include.

Restore the missing binding headers for the 6.18 queue so full arm64 DTB
builds can compile the CIX board device trees.
---
